{
  "stem": "617.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I really don't know whether my parents really believed all the stories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was so unbelievable, which we later found out was very much true.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, that-- at times, my parents were talking that we will go to-- after the Hungarians came in, that we will go to Romania too, because we knew that in Romania, the Jews had it a little better at that time, and they were not going to be sent away.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they were already talk about gathering up the Jews and taking them to ghettos.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as Jews, we had to be much more cautious where we went and how we went.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I said, my father was already afraid to travel too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at times, he would send me to different places for contracts or money collecting or things like that, because it was much safer for me, although I was still very young, to go than for a man, a Jew, you know.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just with the talk and with the worries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in my family, you know, my, my parents tried very much to shelter us, not to have to worry and not to know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very, very good at that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, you know, they wouldn't discuss things in front of us much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I am aware of in, in our places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were not much that I could think of, that any restrictions were-- of course, I'm sure that there were, but I couldn't-- and being a small town made a difference.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not until the 1943, '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
